    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision that the centrifugal blood pump hemolysis performance meets the RH < 1 criterion relative to the predicate device across the five operating conditions evaluated.",
